Introduction

Jang Hyun Soo is a South Korean singer and dancer under P Nation and a member of the boy group TNX. He was first known for competing in the SBS survival show "Loud" where he was also recruited by Psy to be a member of TNX. He made his official debut with the group on May 17, 2022.
